3️⃣ PC Performance Troubleshooting Workflow
User symptom: “My computer is slow.”

🧩 Step-by-step workflow
Check CPU usage

Look for runaway processes

Check RAM usage

Low free RAM = slow apps

Check disk space

Less than 10% free = major slowdown

Check startup apps

Teams, OneDrive, Discord, Steam, etc.

Check Windows Update status

Pending updates slow login and apps

Check key services

Workstation

Server

Windows Update

Check for disk errors

chkdsk /scan

🎯 Resolution examples
Clear temp files

Disable unnecessary startup apps

Restart to complete updates

Recommend RAM upgrade
